<div class="privacy max-w-4xl mx-auto py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="text-center mb-12">
    <h1 class="font-bold text-5xl md:text-6xl mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      At Echo It, your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you visit our website and make a purchase.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Information We Collect -->
  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="font-semibold text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      We collect various types of information to provide a better user experience and to process your orders:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-decimal list-inside pl-4">
      <li><strong>Personal Information</strong>: Name, email address, shipping address, phone number, and payment details when you place an order.</li>
      <li><strong>Usage Data</strong>: Information about how you interact with our website, such as your IP address, browser type, and browsing patterns.</li>
      <li><strong>Cookies</strong>: We use cookies to enhance your experience and personalize the site. Cookies allow us to remember your preferences and settings across sessions.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- How We Use Your Information -->
  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="font-semibold text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      The information we collect is used to improve our services and provide a better customer experience. Specifically, we may use your data for:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-decimal list-inside pl-4">
      <li>Processing your orders and delivering products.</li>
      <li>Communicating with you about your order status, promotions, and offers.</li>
      <li>Personalizing your experience on our website.</li>
      <li>Improving the functionality and content of our website.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- Data Protection -->
  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="font-semibold text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4">Data Protection</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      We take the security of your personal data seriously. To protect your information, we employ the following measures:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-decimal list-inside pl-4">
      <li>Encrypted payment processing to protect your financial details.</li>
      <li>Secure storage of your personal information in accordance with industry standards.</li>
      <li>Regular security audits to prevent unauthorized access.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- Sharing Your Information -->
  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="font-semibold text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4">Sharing Your Information</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes. However, we may share your information in the following cases:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-decimal list-inside pl-4">
      <li><strong>With service providers</strong> who help us process payments and fulfill orders (e.g., shipping companies, payment processors).</li>
      <li><strong>For legal reasons</strong>, such as to comply with a court order or protect the rights of our company.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- Your Rights -->
  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="font-semibold text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      You have the following rights regarding your personal data:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-decimal list-inside pl-4">
      <li>The right to access the personal information we hold about you.</li>
      <li>The right to correct any inaccurate information.</li>
      <li>The right to request the deletion of your personal information.</li>
      <li>The right to opt out of marketing communications at any time.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- Changes to This Privacy Policy -->
  <section class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="font-semibold text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4">Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Us -->
  <section class="text-center">
    <h2 class="font-semibold text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
    <p class="mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy practices, please feel free to contact us at any time.
    </p>
    <%# link_to 'Contact Us', contact_path, class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
  </section>
</div>
